<servinfo servinfosgmlid = "AENAP70A2401003" svcinfotypenbr = "03" svcinfoqualnbr = "01" page = "2" supplyoff = "1" modify = "0">
<title>
Wheels Description
</title>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A2401003001">
<title>
Wheel Maintenance
</title>
<ptxt>
Wheels must be replaced if they have any of the following conditions: bends, dents, excessive lateral or radial runout, air leaks through welds, elongated bolt holes, failure of lug nuts to stay tight, heavy rusts. Wheels with great runout will cause objectionable vibrations.
</ptxt>
